  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "It seems like [api_backend.go](https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/blob/master/eth/api_backend.go#L284-L286) marks transactions coming from [SendRawTransaction](https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/blob/master/internal/ethapi/api.go#L1940-L1946) as `local`. \r\n\r\nThe side-effect of this is that the [legacypool](https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/blob/master/core/txpool/legacypool/legacypool.go#L588-L590) sets the `MinTip` to zero, before calling the validation logic, so it's not possible to enforce a minimum gas price in the miner.",
